## Stage Architecture

||| Stage | Name | Trigger | Input Material | Output Dir | Failure Report |
||-------|------|---------|---------------|-----------|----------------|
||| **S1** | 需求评审 | `/aidocx-s1-review` | 原始需求文档 | `<req_name>/「S1 需求评审」/` | `fail_report_S1.md` |
||| **S1.5** | 业务澄清与准出 | — | clarification_checklist（人工填写） | `<req_name>/「S1 需求评审」/` | `fail_report_S1_5.md` |
||| **S2** | 需求拆解 | `/aidocx-s2-breakdown` | S1.5 exit_permission + 终版需求.md | `<req_name>/「S2 需求拆解」/` | `fail_report_S2.md` + `requirement_objects.md/json` |
||| **S2.5** | 迭代规划 ⚙️opt-in | `/aidocx-s2-5-iteration` | S2 backlog | `<req_name>/「S2.5 迭代规划」/` | `fail_report_S2_5.md` |
||| **S3** | 原型导出 | `/aidocx-s3-prototype` | S2 backlog | `<req_name>/「S3 原型导出」/` | `fail_report_S3.md` |
||| **S4** | 流程图导出 | `/aidocx-s4-flowchart` | S2 backlog + S3 prototype | `<req_name>/「S4 流程图导出」/` | `fail_report_S4.md` |
||| **S5** | 测试点生成 | `/aidocx-s5-test-points` | S2 backlog | `<req_name>/「S5 测试点生成」/` | `fail_report_S5.md` |
||| **S6** | 测试用例生成 | `/aidocx-s6-test-cases` | S5 test_points.json | `<req_name>/「S6 测试用例生成」/` | `fail_report_S6.md` |
||| **S7** | 用例审查 | `/aidocx-s7-review` | S6 test_cases.json | `<req_name>/「S6 测试用例生成」/` | `fail_report_S7.md` |
||| **S8** | 自迭代 | `/aidocx-s8-self-iteration` | S7 review_report + feedback_logs | `<req_name>/「S8 自迭代」/` | `fail_report_S8.md` |

